HI all,
		I just would like to know if there is any plan
to "split" ipv6 support from ipv4. Right now is not possible
to compile ipv6 without ipv4. It would be nice to be able to
build ipv6 only boxes. Specially right now that ipv6 starts to
be more and more available.
Thanks
